name: GU Roctane Cold Brew Coffee
description: But first coffee. A cold-brew pick-me-up to crush your workout.Roctane blend is fuel for activities that require focus, concentration and sustained mental acuity. Contains up to three times as much sodium (depending on flavor), and three times as many branched-chain amino acids as original Gu gels.Contains 70mg of caffeine.Ingredients: maltodextrin, water, fructose, leucine, taurine, sodium citrate, valine, natural flavor, potassium citrate, green tea leaf extract (contains caffeine), citric acid, calcium carbonate, beta-alanine, isoleucine, sea salt, gellan gum, medium chain triglycerides, sodium benzoate, potassium sorbate.
